+| AlphaMissense scores | hegelab.org per-protein TSVs | 2026-02-16 | Cheng et al., Science 2023 |
+| ClinVar classifications | NCBI E-utilities API | 2026-02-16 | Pathogenic/LP + Benign/LB only |
