-### 8.1 Age-Adjusted Cox
-Model: `OS ~ has_am_pathogenic + age_scaled, strata = tumor`. Age pulled from cBioPortal clinical data (98% available). Result: HR changes by < 0.1%, indicating minimal confounding by age.
